    <descript>
      <abstract>The polygon layer represents the group of residential parcels intentionally created together by a land developer. These areas may or may not have an Home Owners Association (HOA) governing them.</abstract>
      <purpose>To be used as cartographic overlay in maps requiring subdivision information also used as overlay in Web applications</purpose>
